headline: Oracle Textura Surpasses $1 Trillion in Construction Payments Processed
summary: Oracle Textura Payment Management Cloud Service has now processed over $1 trillion in construction payments to subcontractors. This milestone represents work on more than 120,000 projects from over 800 general contractors and project owners, and over 200,000 subcontractors since Textura first launched in 2006.
